    dc:description "FIGURES 1–4. Lestiphorus yamatonis Tsuneki (from Kunashir Isl.): 1—habitus, ♀; 2—propodeum and metasomal base, dor- solateral view, ♀; 3–4—head, frontal view, ♀ (3), ♂ (4)." ;
