    dc:description "FIGURES 5–9. Lestiphorus. 5, 7–9—L. bilunulatus A. Costa (5, 7, 8—from Primorsky Terr., Russia, 9—fromAmur Prov., Russia); 6—L. yamatonis Tsuneki (from Kunashir Isl.); 5, 6—mesosoma, ventrolateral view, ♀; 7—metasoma, dorsolateral view, ♀; 8, 9—head, frontal view, ♀ (8), ♂ (9)." ;
